verse.lines:
{lang-eng}On that cross, alone, forsaken,
Where no pity’ng eye was found;
Now, to God’s right hand exalted,
With Thy praise the heavens resound.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Gazing on it we adore Thee,
Blessed, precious, holy Lord;
Thou the Lamb, alone art worthy—
This be earth’s and heaven’s accord.{/lang-eng}
